snippet.title: "Dark Clouds" At Dutch Festival "Pinkpop" Metallica Performance

localized.description: The Photoshopped picture does not give justice to the "Dark Clouds of Demons" over the "Pinkpop Festival" http://www.nltimes.nl/2014/06/10/five-killed-storms-pinkpop-ignore-warnings/ Just before Metallica preformed at "Pinkpop Festival" a dark demonic cloud and thunderstorm rolled in on Pentecost Weekend http://beforeitsnews.com/paranormal/2014/06/demon-clouds-at-dutch-festival-pinkpop-metallica-performance-video-2470366.html  it is always possible this picture could have been photoshopped but the event and the storm did take place I was not there but it has been reported by some outlets  http://www.paulbegleyprophecy.com also http://www.liveleak.com/view?i=658_1402345159#R014eHR6OKv34uEc.01 also http://www.dutchnews.nl/news/archives/2014/06/pinkpop_ends_late_but_survives.php
